semplice-zuki-themes (1.4.7-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * [gtk-3.0] Fix overshoot declaration
  * [gtk-3.0] Fix ComboBox font color. Fixes #1
  * [gtk-3.0] Remove box-shadow from TreeView rows. Fixes #2
  * [gtk-3.0] Fix file picker sidebar. Fixes #3
  * [gtk-3.0] Remove outlines on focus. Contributes to #8
  * [gtk-3.0] Fix linked buttons
  * [gtk-3.0] Remove unnecessary background-color on buttons needing attention, and mark them with the vera-color. Fixes #7.
  * [gtk-3.0] Make the color chooser buttons flat. Fixes #4.
  * [gtk-3.0] Add some padding to list rows. Contributes to #5.
  * [gtk-3.0] CSD tweaks

