semplice-zuki-themes (1.4-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * gtk-2.0: made buttons and checks/radios more color-agnostic.
  * gtk-3.0: compile theme into a gresource file to speed-up load times.
  * debian/rules: ensure we call compile_gtk3_theme.sh and clean.sh when needed.
  * debian/control: build-depend on libgtk-3-dev, libglib2.0-dev, libgdk-pixbuf2.0-dev
    and libxml2-utils to be able to compile the gtk-3.0 theme into a gresource file.
  * debian/: do not ship the entire gtk-3.0 directory, use instead the gresource.

 -- Eugenio Paolantonio (g7) <me@medesimo.eu>  Sun, 22 Feb 2015 11:58:11 +0100

